    %% User-facing roles
    NotebooksEdit -->|"get,list,watch,create,delete,<br/>deletecollection,patch,update"| Notebooks
    NotebooksView -->|"get,list,watch"| Notebooks
    NotebooksAdmin -->|"aggregates"| NotebooksEdit

